headline: GTA Online
subtitle: Unlock the Dinka Tee and Neon Stitch Emissive Mask
content:
To celebrate the release of the Verus, get your brand coordination on point with the free Dinka Tee, awarded for playing at any point this week.

Completing any Casino Work over the next seven days will also bag you the Neon Stitch Emissive Mask. Give Ms. Baker a call on your iFruit to get started, and come back after March 1st to receive your award (all awards should be delivered within 72 hours).
